query:
SELECT s.id, s.plantProfile, COUNT(m.id) as message_count, COUNT(mt.id) as metric_count 
FROM sessions s 
LEFT JOIN messages m ON s.id = m.sessionId 
LEFT JOIN metrics mt ON s.id = mt.sessionId 
WHERE s.isTestData = true 
GROUP BY s.id 
ORDER BY s.id DESC 
LIMIT 5;
